      "content": {
        "title": "Extensor Tendon Injuries and Repair — Core Principles",
        "definition": "Disruption of extensor tendons over the dorsum of the hand and wrist from laceration or attrition.",
        "summary": "Extensor zones guide repair approach. Mallet finger may be managed with splinting; sagittal band rupture causes extensor subluxation."
      },
